name: Little Earths: Many Earths
description:
We’re just little specks of dust floating on a not-so-giant rock. The universe is a vast expanse of endless possibilities, numerous wonders, unlimited worlds.

So why do we choose to live in only one world when we can live in many?

PS: Aliens not included (yet).

*This is a free drop to the primary collectors of Little Earths #1-3*
